value to not change in time.

00:28:08.200 --> 00:28:11.420
In general, for any
operator A, the time rate

00:28:11.420 --> 00:28:14.430
of change of its
expectation value

00:28:14.430 --> 00:28:27.840
is given by the
commutator of E with A.

00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:30.690
I can do the symbols-- good.

00:28:30.690 --> 00:28:35.880
OK, so in particular, if
this commutator vanishes,

00:28:35.880 --> 00:28:41.660
if the commutator vanishes--
equals 0--, this is equal to--

